                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method and application of monatomic copper catalyst anchored and modified by carbon nitride and magnesium-aluminum double-layer structure",
                    "一种氮化碳和镁铝双层状结构锚定与修饰单原子铜催化剂的制备方法及应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a preparation method and application of a monatomic copper catalyst anchored and modified by a carbon nitride and magnesium-aluminum double-layer structure, the preparation method comprises the following steps: respectively preparing carbon nitride and magnesium-aluminum layered structure materials, combining the two materials, dispersing the combined double-layer structure material into deionized water, adding copper nitrate and urea, and uniformly stirring to obtain the monatomic copper catalyst anchored and modified by the carbon nitride and magnesium-aluminum double-layer structure. A solid mixture is obtained through stirring, oil bath evaporation drying and grinding, the solid mixture is subjected to reduction treatment in the atmosphere of hydrogen in nitrogen to obtain the catalyst, the catalyst is applied to a furfural hydrogenation reaction, the furfural conversion rate and the furfuryl alcohol yield can reach 99% or above, and the defect that a traditional copper-based catalyst is low in conversion rate is overcome; the monatomic copper catalyst is simple in preparation method, high in atom utilization rate and excellent in catalytic performance, furfural can be catalytically converted into high-value sustainable value-added chemicals, and based on the characteristics, the catalyst has huge application potential in the fields of biomass energy conversion, carbon dioxide reduction, environment restoration and the like."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种氮化碳和镁铝双层状结构锚定与修饰单原子铜催化剂的制备方法及应用，分别制备氮化碳和镁铝层状结构材料，将两种材料进行组合，组合后的双层状结构材料分散到去离子水中，加入硝酸铜、尿素，搅拌、油浴蒸干、研磨得到固体混合物，将固体混合物在氮中氢的气氛下还原处理，得到催化剂，将催化剂应用于糠醛加氢反应，可实现糠醛转化率和糠醇产率达到99％以上，改善了传统铜基催化剂转化率低的缺点；本发明提供一种制备方法简单、原子利用率高、催化性能优异的单原子铜催化剂，可将糠醛催化转化为高价值的可持续增值化学品，基于这些特性，该催化剂在生物质能转化、二氧化碳还原、环境修复等诸多领域都有着巨大的应用潜力。"
                }
            ]
